313
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:52,350
What are you doing here?

314
00:15:54,280 --> 00:15:56,470
Is Miss Wu with you?

315
00:15:56,470 --> 00:15:57,710
No... no... she isn’t.

316
00:15:57,710 --> 00:15:59,030
We parted long ago

317
00:15:59,030 --> 00:16:01,760
