deliver Mr. Li’s message.

318
00:16:01,760 --> 00:16:02,790
What message?

319
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:06,030
Where are you going?

320
00:16:06,030 --> 00:16:07,440
I’m not done yet.

321
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:08,880
