323
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:11,640
Mr. Zhu is also here?

324
00:16:14,470 --> 00:16:15,280
Ying’er.

325
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:20,790
Sir,

326
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:22,640
